\delta_0*\phi=\phi
 (\delta_0 * \phi)(x) = \delta_0[\phi(x-\cdot)] = \phi(x-0)=\phi(x),
\langle \delta_0,\phi\rangle = \phi(0)
(\delta_0\ast\phi)(x) = \langle \delta_0,\phi_x\rangle
\phi_x(t) = \phi(x-t)
(\delta_0\ast\phi)(x) = \phi_x(0) = \phi(x)
